<br/>
Thank you to @whw_what.how.for.whom for the recommendation, and to @ninakurtela for taking me to Dotrščina Memorial Park just outside Zagreb, where several of Bakić’s powerful works are set within the landscape.</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DUMGnt5jCvq/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
